Class MessageNotReadableException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • javax.jms.JMSException
          • javax.jms.MessageNotReadableException
            • com.sun.messaging.jms.MessageNotReadableException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sun.messaging.jmq.jmsclient.logging.Loggable, java.io.Serializable

    public class MessageNotReadableException
extends MessageNotReadableException
implements com.sun.messaging.jmq.jmsclient.logging.Loggable

    This exception must be thrown when a JMS client attempts to read a write-only message.
